Ex-Marvell Technology Accountant Ng in Plea Talks, Set for Arraignment

-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 
2011-12-07T14:47:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/ex-marvell-technology-accountant-ng-in-plea-talks-set-for-arraignment.html
Former  Marvell Technology Group Ltd. (MRVL) 
accountant Stanley Ng, charged in a nationwide crackdown on
 insider trading , is in plea discussions with U.S. prosecutors,
according to a notation on his case docket dated Nov. 28.  Ng is scheduled to be arraigned today in Manhattan federal
court, according to a court clerk.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Van Voris in New York at 
 rvanvoris@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
